data.description: Don't miss this 3 bedroom, 3 bath Ranch located in Marshalltown's Northwest side! This home boasts 2,165 total square feet! Step inside, and you'll be greeted by an inviting living space with charming built-ins, hardwood flooring and natural light. The home's layout connects the formal living to the galley kitchen & dining room and on the other side walk through the living room to find the 3 bedrooms and full bath, making it an ideal separate space for entertaining and enjoying. The kitchen has newer stainless-steel appliances with abundant cabinetry. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing ample space for relaxation and personalization, plus a walk-in closet! The finished basement offers plenty of versatile space with endless possibilities- family room, workout space, you name it! The covered deck and fenced-in yard with patio provide the perfect outdoor oasis; Parking is a breeze with an attached garage. ACHOSA Buyer Home Warranty plan included! Call today for your private tour!
